        <briefdescription>
<para>MGMT_EVT_[...] Event ID for handler to be called on. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This has special meaning if <ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api_1ggaab6470007be89e5aab88838456f9561aaf9e289ad5f7e0fd8bec581f67951813a" kindref="member">MGMT_EVT_OP_ALL</ref> is used (which will cover all events for all groups), or MGMT_EVT_OP_*_MGMT_ALL (which will cover all events for a single group). For events that are part of a single group, they can be or&apos;d together for this to have one registration trigger on multiple events, please note that this will only work for a single group, to register for events in different groups, they must be registered separately. </para>
